name: Rustic Handstamped Hammered Gold Wedding Ring
description: This is a beautifully hand forged 14k solid gold ring made from flat stock that is 1.5mm thick and 8mm wide. Totally unique and stamped with a simple design, shown here, an "iron cross" or "maltese cross". Your guy will love this unique wedding ring. I can make your ring in any size including 1/2 and 1/4 sizes. I add in approximately 1/2 size to this ring. Give me your "normal" ring size and I'll add in the appropriate amount of ease. If you're not sure of your size, please purchase one of my ring sizers and use it to size your finger. If you use my ring sizer to determine your size, I guarantee your ring will fit or I'll resize it for free. All my designs are made to order unless otherwise noted. After you purchase I will contact you to give you a "ship-by" date and make sure I have your size and personalization request. Solid gold orders are sent via Fedex Ground with signature required. Check my bio and feedback rating at Etsy.com.

name: Primitive Hammered 14k Gold Narrow Band
description: Beautifully hand faceted yellow gold ring I fashioned from 2.5mm x 1.23mm stock. Perfectly simply and unique - lightweight but with a definite presence on your finger. This would be a very nice minimalist wedding band for a man or a woman. I can make this set in any size for you, including 1/4 and 1/2 sizes. You can contact me with the size you need after you order, or I will contact you. All my designs are made to order unless otherwise noted. After you purchase I will contact you to give you a "ship-by" date and make sure I have your size and personalization request. Solid gold orders are sent via Fedex Ground with signature required. name: Rose Gold Twist and Wide Sterling Band Ring Set
description:
This eclectic set includes a 1mm hand-twisted solid 14k gold ring, and a 10mm x 1mm hammered sterling silver band that can be personalized on the inside with a word or two of your choice.

It's beautifully feminine but not girly. 

I can make this set in any size for you, including 1/4 and 1/2 sizes. You can contact me with the size you need after you order, or I will contact you.

All my designs are made to order unless otherwise noted. After you purchase I will contact you to give you a "ship-by" date and make sure I have your size and personalization request.

Solid gold orders are sent via Fedex Ground with signature required.

name: Artisan Sterling Silver "Braveheart" Ring
description:
As rustic and archaic as it can be, and full of rugged beauty. This artisan designed ring is custom made to your size and looks smashing on a man or a woman. The ring is 3/8" wide and a full 1.5mm thick. Substantial. Unique - each one is slightly different and made especially for you.

Contact me with your ring size.
